p: Dengue and chikungunya incidence from Tegucigalpa (city) for the year 2015 were taken from the study by Zambrano et al. ( 2017) with permission from Elsevier (license number 4576391190534). Counts were collected by the national surveillance system and refer to cases clinically and laboratory confirmed (by serology and RT‐PCR). Data series were extracted from Figure 5 using Engauge Digitizer Software V10.4 ( https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2585387).
